high_descs: Turn to the right, move to the stove, turn left, so the stove is on the right and counter in front.
Pick up the knife on the right.
Turn from the counter and move to the refrigerator.
Use the knife and slice the potato on the top shelf of the refrigerator.
Turn from the refrigerator and move to the counter near the two plants.
Place the knife on to the plate.
Turn from the counter and move to the refrigerator.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Turn from the refrigerator and move to the counter near the two plants.
Place the potato slice on to the plate.
Pick up the plate with the knife and potato slice on it.
Turn from the counter and move to the refrigerator.
Place the plate on to the top shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of potato onto a plate, place the plate into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the stove then turn left to the counter.
Pick the knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, cut the potato inside, and close the fridge.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right again and walk to the counter.
Place the knife on the plate on the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, take out a potato slice, and close the fridge.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right again and walk to the counter.
Place the potato slice in front of the knife on the plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate with the potato slice and knife on it.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the plate inside, and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a potato slice and knife on it into the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Go across the room to the refrigerator.
Open the fridge and cut the potato on the shelf.
Take the butter knife to the counter with the plants.
Set the butter knife down on the white plate.
Go back to the fridge.
Take a piece of the sliced potato out of the fridge.
Take the potato slice to the counter with the plants.
Set the potato slice on the plate with the butter knife.
Pick up the plate with the knife and potato slice on it.
Go across the room to the fridge.
Put the plate with the potato slice and butter knife in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate in the fridge with a potato slice next to a butter knife on it.
